beer.beer_description:
First brewed for release at the Great Australian Beer SpecTAPular 2014 (GABS). 'Breaking The Cardinal Rule' is a big bold Belgian inspired IPA Tripel. 'New world' US hops meld harmoniously with the traditional malty sweetness and Belgian yeast strain derived complexity of a 'classic' Tripel.
HOPS: Citra, Centennial and Columbus
80IBUs
